text: The Last Days of Chez Nous is a 1992 Australian drama movie directed by Gillian Armstrong and starring Lisa Harrow, Bruno Ganz, Kerry Fox, Miranda Otto, Lex Marinos. It was distributed by Fine Line Features. ==Other websites== * * Category:1992 drama movies Category:Australian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Gillian Armstrong
title: The Last Days of Chez Nous
